alphabet.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who is learning the alphabet;
hence, a tyro.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One engaged in teaching the alphabet.</def>
